verbose_text: Martin et al showed that 6% NaOCl significantly reduced the survival and odontogenic differentiation of apical papilla stem cells while 1.5% NaOCl increased the expression of DSPP in stem cells.15 After disinfection, it is recommended to use intracanal medicaments, either Ca (OH) 2 or triple paste antibiotic (TAP).
